# Database Migration Skill

> **Trigger**: Use this skill when asked to create, apply, run, or roll back database migrations, or when schema changes are needed.

## ORM & Database

- ORM: {{ORM}}
- Database: {{DB_TYPE}}
- Schema location: `{{SCHEMA_DIR}}/`
- Migrations directory: `{{MIGRATIONS_DIR}}/`

## Create a Migration

```bash
# After editing schema file
{{CMD_MIGRATE_GENERATE}} --name {{MIGRATION_NAME_CONVENTION}}
```

{{MIGRATION_NAMING_NOTE}}
